Package: duckdbfs
Title: High Performance Remote Filesystem Access Using "duckdb"
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
  person("Carl", "Boettiger", , "cboettig@gmail.com", c("aut", "cre"),
         comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1642-628X"))
Description: Provides friendly wrappers for creating duckdb-backed connections
  to tabular datasets (csv, tsv, parquet, etc) on local or remote filesystems.
  This mimics the behaviour of "open_dataset" in the arrow package, 
  but in addition to "S3" filesystem also generalizes to any list of http urls.
